{
  "name": "RPlog_Conversation_with_a_Verpine",
  "title": "A Conversation with a Verpine",
  "summary": "In Fountain Square at the heart of Plaxton City, the Jedi Jessalyn people-watches by the old fountain when Vzzee, a Verpine salesbeing and technician for Rendili Shipyards she had met earlier at the spaceport, stops to greet her. They chat about ship repairs and power nodes until Orson Tighe, a ship mechanic and Jessalyn's close friend, arrives and surprises everyone by greeting Vzzee in fluent Verpine. The three mechanics trade banter about ships, with Vzzee pitching Rendili's Kale Light Cruiser and trade-in offers while gently fielding Orson's prodding questions. The mood is warm and playful, full of inside jokes between Orson and Jessalyn, until Jessalyn mentions an appointment they must keep. The two friends bid Vzzee a friendly farewell and head off together.",
